pakage com.hsbc.training.app contains mainApp.java to execute the application.
pakage com.hsbc.training.app.dao includes files shoppingDao.java as interface and DuplicateItemException.java and ItemNotFoundException.java as exception for the application.
package com.hsbc.training.app.entity includes Apparels.java, Electronics.java and FoodItems.java as the entity for the application.
package com.hsbc.training.app.impl includes shoppingDaoImpl.java implementing shoppingDao.java as the implementation for the service layer of the application.
package com.hsbc.training.app.service includes ShoppingService.java as the service layer of the application.

In the calculations Ive assumed the maximum quantity f any item is 200, for finding the sale.
